[2;36m                    [0m         [39m===[0m[33mIssue[0m[39m===[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mERROR: libFuzzer: timeout[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m===Evaluation [0m[33mReport[0m[39m===[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m# Evaluation Report[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Summary[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mA libFuzzer run terminated with a timeout error. During fuzzing, the session [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mexceeded the allotted execution time for a test case or for the overall fuzzing [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mjob, causing libFuzzer to abort with the message “ERROR: libFuzzer: timeout.”[0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Description[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Issue without cause speculation  [0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  The reported issue is that libFuzzer stopped fuzzing because it hit a predefined [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtime limit. There was no crash, memory corruption, or sanitizer report—only a [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtimeout indication.[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Vulnerability type  [0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  No specific vulnerability or crash was reported. This is a performance/hang [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mindicator rather than a security fault such as a buffer overflow or use-after-free.[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Important observations and findings  [0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • The fuzzer reached its execution time cap, suggesting one or more inputs [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtriggered a long-running or unbounded loop in the code under test.  [0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • The harness serves as the entry point for libFuzzer but is not the root cause; [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mit simply feeds test inputs into the target code.  [0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • No sanitizer or leak errors accompanied the timeout message, indicating no [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mimmediate memory safety violation was detected.  [0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • The timeout could occur on a single slow test case or be the aggregate result [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mof many slow executions.[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Code areas to investigate for a holistic view  [0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m. Fuzzer configuration and invocation flags [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g., `-[0m[33mtimeout[0m[39m=` setting[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m to [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mconfirm time limits.  [0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m. The harness function [0m[1;39m([0m[39moften `LLVMFuzzerTestOneInput` or equivalent[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m to [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39midentify which module’s API is exercised.  [0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;36m3[0m[39m. Functions called by the harness—especially loops, recursive routines, or [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcomplex parsing logic that may not terminate promptly.  [0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m. Input-handling routines or parsers that may enter pathological states on [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcertain inputs.  [0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;36m5[0m[39m. Resource-intensive subsystems [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g., cryptography, compression, I/O[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m that [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcould cause prolonged execution.  [0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;36m6[0m[39m. Any custom instrumentation or signal handlers that interact with libFuzzer’s [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtiming mechanism.[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Initial Issue Log[0m                                                                [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m198[0m[39m:                 * allow [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m [0m[32m"."[0m[39m and [0m[32m"-"[0m[39m and [0m[32m"+"[0m[39m at start of number. *[0m[35m/[0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m199[0m[39m:                StringBuilder buf = new [0m[1;35mStringBuilder[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m200[0m[39m:                [0m[1;35mbuf.append[0m[1;39m([0m[39m c [0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m36[0m[39m:     * Write CR and/or LF that were kept, then writes len bytes from the [0m        [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m184[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m185[0m[39m:        [0m[1;35msuper[0m[1;39m([0m[39msource[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m186[0m[39m:        this.password = password;[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m187[0m[39m:        this.keyAlias = keyAlias;[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m188[0m[39m:        fileLen = [0m[1;35msource.length[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m189[0m[39m:        keyStoreInputStream = keyStore;[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m190[0m[39m:        [0m[1;35minit[0m[1;39m([0m[39mstreamCacheCreateFunction[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m191[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m192[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m193[0m[39m:    private void [0m[1;35minit[0m[1;39m([0m[39mStreamCacheCreateFunction streamCacheCreateFunction[0m[1;39m)[0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m194[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m195[0m[39m:        String eofLookupRangeStr = [0m[1;35mSystem.getProperty[0m[1;39m([0m[39mSYSPROP_EOFLOOKUPRANGE[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m196[0m[39m:        if [0m[1;39m([0m[39meofLookupRangeStr != null[0m[1;39m)[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m197[0m[39m:        [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m198[0m[39m:            try[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m199[0m[39m:            [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m200[0m[39m:                [0m[1;35msetEOFLookupRange[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mInteger.parseInt[0m[1;39m([0m[39meofLookupRangeStr[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m201[0m[39m:            [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m202[0m[39m:            catch [0m[1;39m([0m[39mNumberFormatException nfe[0m[1;39m)[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m203[0m[39m:            [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m204[0m[39m:                [0m[1;35mLOG.warn[0m[1;39m([0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m205[0m[39m:                        [0m[32m"System property "[0m[39m + SYSPROP_EOFLOOKUPRANGE + [0m[32m" does [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [32mnot contain an integer value, but: '[0m[32m{[0m[32m}[0m[32m'"[0m[39m,[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m206[0m[39m:                        eofLookupRangeStr[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m207[0m[39m:            [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m208[0m[39m:        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m209[0m[39m:        document = new [0m[1;35mCOSDocument[0m[1;39m([0m[39mstreamCacheCreateFunction, this[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m210[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m211[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m212[0m[39m:    [0m[35m/[0m[39m**[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m213[0m[39m:     * Sets how many trailing bytes of PDF file are searched for EOF marker and[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [32m'startxref'[0m[39m marker. If not set we use[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m214[0m[39m:     * default value [0m[1;39m{[0m[39m@link #DEFAULT_TRAIL_BYTECOUNT[0m[1;39m}[0m[39m.[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m215[0m[39m:     * [0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m216[0m[39m:     * <p>We check that new value is at least [0m[1;36m16[0m[39m. However for practical use [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcases this value should not be lower than[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m217[0m[39m:     * [0m[1;36m1000[0m[39m; even [0m[1;36m2000[0m[39m was found to not be enough in some cases where some [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtrailing garbage like HTML snippets followed[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m218[0m[39m:     * the EOF marker.<[0m[35m/[0m[95mp[0m[39m>[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m219[0m[39m:     * [0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m220[0m[39m:     * <p>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m221[0m[39m:     * In case system property [0m[1;39m{[0m[39m@link #SYSPROP_EOFLOOKUPRANGE[0m[1;39m}[0m[39m is defined this [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mvalue will be set on initialization but[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m222[0m[39m:     * can be overwritten later.[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m223[0m[39m:     * <[0m[35m/[0m[95mp[0m[39m>[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m224[0m[39m:     * [0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m225[0m[39m:     * @param byteCount number of trailing bytes[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m226[0m[39m:     *[0m[35m/[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m227[0m[39m:    public void [0m[1;35msetEOFLookupRange[0m[1;39m([0m[39mint byteCount[0m[1;39m)[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m228[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m229[0m[39m:        if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mbyteCount > [0m[1;36m15[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m230[0m[39m:        [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code>[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpdfbox/src/main/java/org/apache/pdfbox/pdfparser/PDFParser.jav[0m[1;92ma:236[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m236[0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m236[0m[39m:[0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_snippets[0m[39m>[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAfter analyzing the parser internals, two unbounded code paths can stall on [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmalformed PDFs and explain the fuzzer timeout:[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. **Unbounded “endstream” scanning**  [0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   In BaseParser.parseCOSStream [0m[1;39m([0m[39minvoked after reading a stream dictionary[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, the [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcode falls back to scanning byte-by-byte for the literal “endstream” marker if the [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[35m/[0m[95mLength[0m[39m` entry is missing or incorrect. When a crafted input omits “endstream” or [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msets `[0m[35m/[0m[95mLength[0m[39m` to an unreasonable value, the parser will read until EOF, causing an[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39marbitrarily long hang.[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. **Unbounded page-tree recursion**  [0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   In PDFParser.initialParse → checkPages, the code walks the page-tree via each [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mnode’s `[0m[35m/[0m[95mKids[0m[39m` arrays without tracking already-visited dictionaries or bounding the[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdepth/size of the tree. A deeply nested or cyclic `[0m[35m/[0m[95mPages[0m[39m` structure can trigger [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mvery deep recursion or repeated revisits, again leading to excessive parse times [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mand eventual timeout.[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mTo address both without touching harness, test code, or third-party libraries, [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mimplement these two safe-guards in the core parser:[0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mStep [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m: **Bound the stream-data read by `[0m[35m/[0m[95mLength[0m[39m`.**  [0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- In BaseParser [0m[1;39m([0m[39mwhere parseCOSStream is implemented[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, after parsing the stream [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdictionary and before calling the slow endstream-scan helper:[0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  a[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m Look up the `[0m[35m/[0m[95mLength[0m[39m` entry:  [0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     COSBase lenObj = [0m[1;35mdict.getItem[0m[1;39m([0m[39mCOSName.LENGTH[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;  [0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlenObj instanceof COSInteger[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m[39m  [0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       long length = [0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m([0m[39mCOSInteger[0m[1;39m)[0m[39mlenObj[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.longValue[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;  [0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlength >= [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m && length <= [0m[1;35msource.length[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m - [0m[1;35msource.getPosition[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m[39m  [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m fast path: read exactly `length` bytes from source [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g., via a [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mRandomAccessReadView or readFully[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         byte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[39m data = new byte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m([0m[39mint[0m[1;39m)[0m[39mlength[0m[1;39m][0m[39m;  [0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[1;35msource.read[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;  [0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m attach data as stream contents  [0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[1;35mskipWhiteSpaces[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;  [0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         return new [0m[1;35mCOSStream[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdict, data[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;  [0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       [0m[1;39m}[0m[39m  [0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;39m}[0m[39m  [0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  b[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m Only if `[0m[35m/[0m[95mLength[0m[39m` is absent or invalid, fall back to the existing endstream [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mscan, but cap the scan at a reasonable maximum [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g., [0m[1;36m10[0m[39m MB or a fraction of the [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfile length[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     − Modify the helper [0m[1;39m([0m[39mreadUntilEndStream or EndstreamFilterStream[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m to accept a [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmaxBytes parameter and abort the scan [0m[1;39m([0m[39mthrow an IOException or return partial data[0m[1;39m)[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mif exceeded.  [0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     − Use the lesser of fileLen or a hard‐coded ceiling [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g., [0m[1;36m10[0m[39m * [0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mDEFAULT_TRAIL_BYTECOUNT[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m to avoid unbounded loops.[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mStep [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m: **Guard the page-tree traversal.**  [0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- In COSParser [0m[1;39m([0m[39mor PDFParser where `[0m[1;35mcheckPages[0m[1;39m([0m[39mCOSDictionary[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` is declared[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:[0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  a[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m Introduce a per-parse, in‐memory Set<COSObjectKey> `visitedPages` and an int [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`nodeCount`.  [0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  b[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m Overload `checkPages`:[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     public void [0m[1;35mcheckPages[0m[1;39m([0m[39mCOSDictionary root[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m throws IOException [0m[1;39m{[0m[39m  [0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         Set<COSObjectKey> visited = new HashSet<>[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;  [0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[1;35mcheckPagesRec[0m[1;39m([0m[39mroot, visited, [0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;  [0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;39m}[0m[39m  [0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  c[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m In the private recursive helper `[0m[1;35mcheckPagesRec[0m[1;39m([0m[39mCOSDictionary node, [0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mSet<COSObjectKey> visited, int depth[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`:  [0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     − If depth exceeds a threshold [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g., [0m[1;36m1000[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m or [0m[1;35mvisited.size[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m exceeds a [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mceiling [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g., [0m[1;36m5000[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, abort recursion with an IOException or log a warning and [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mreturn to avoid further descent.  [0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     − If this node maps to a COSObjectKey [0m[1;39m([0m[39mvia [0m[1;35mnode.getCOSObject[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.getKey[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcheck if it’s already in `visited`; if so, return immediately. Otherwise add it to [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`visited`.  [0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     − Then read `[0m[35m/[0m[95mType[0m[39m` and, if it’s a Pages node, extract `[0m[35m/[0m[95mKids[0m[39m`, dereference [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39meach to a COSDictionary and recurse with depth+[0m[1;36m1[0m[39m.  [0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     − If it’s a Page leaf, perform the existing leaf checks [0m[1;39m([0m[39mno change[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mStep [0m[1;36m3[0m[39m: **Preserve existing behavior and leniency flags.**  [0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Both patches respect `[0m[1;35misLenient[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`: if lenient mode is active, you may lower the [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mstrictness of failures [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g., treat an endstream‐scan overrun as a warning[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m. In [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mstrict mode, throw an IOException immediately.  [0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The new logic never alters public APIs or harness code; it merely restricts [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpathological loops within the parser. Existing tests and downstream PRs are [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39munaffected.[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mStep [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m: **Validation and side-effect mitigation.**  [0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Unit tests for parsing small, valid PDFs must still pass without triggering the [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mnew bounds. Choose thresholds [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g., length ≤ fileLen, depth ≤ [0m[1;36m1000[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m high enough [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthat legitimate documents are unaffected.  [0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Add new fuzz tests with PDFs having missing “endstream” markers or cyclic page [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtrees to assert that an IOException [0m[1;39m([0m[39mrather than a hang[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m occurs.  [0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Document the new parser flags [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g., MAX_STREAM_SCAN, MAX_PAGE_DEPTH[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m in the [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdeveloper guide so integrators can adjust them if necessary.[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mJustification:  [0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Bounding the stream scan by `[0m[35m/[0m[95mLength[0m[39m` aligns with the PDF spec’s intent and [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprevents degenerate inputs from causing linear‐time scans per stream.  [0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Tracking visited page nodes and capping page-tree depth protects against [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpathological or cyclic page hierarchies that could otherwise cause exponential-time[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mor infinite recursion.  [0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Both enhancements operate entirely within the PDFBox core, preserve existing [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfunctionality for well-formed PDFs, and eliminate unbounded loops that lead to [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfuzzer timeouts.  [0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mfix_strategy[0m[1m>[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ===Evaluation [33mEnd[0m===                                                                [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m===[0m[33mIssue[0m[39m===[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mERROR: libFuzzer: timeout[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m===Evaluation [0m[33mReport[0m[39m===[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m# Evaluation Report[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Summary[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Initial issue: A libFuzzer run against PDFBox reported a “timeout” error, [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mindicating the parser hung or took too long on certain inputs.[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Patch attempt: [0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  - In EndstreamFilterStream, introduced a `MAX_STREAM_SCAN` cap [0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m10[0m[39m MB[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m and [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmodified the `filter` method to disable filtering when the scanned length would [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mexceed the cap.[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  - In PDFParser, replaced the unbounded `checkPages` call with a new [0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`safeCheckPages` method that tracks visited page‐tree nodes and enforces limits on [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtree depth [0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m1[0m[39m [0m[1;36m000[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m and total nodes [0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m5[0m[39m [0m[1;36m000[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m. This involved adding imports for `Set`,[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`HashSet`, `COSObject`, `COSObjectKey`, and `COSArray`, plus the recursive helper [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`checkPagesRec`.[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Patch result: Compilation of PDFBox failed with errors in `PDFParser.java`, [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mchiefly:[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  - Incompatible types: `COSBase` cannot be converted to `COSObject`.[0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  - Several “cannot find symbol: class COSBase” errors in the new recursive method.[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Description[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Initial issue  [0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The test harness reported a `libFuzzer: timeout` while exercising PDF parsing [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcode.  [0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - No stack trace was provided, but timeouts often point to unbounded loops or [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39moverly deep recursion.[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Observations on the issue  [0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The EndstreamFilterStream’s fallback path can scan arbitrarily large streams, [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpotentially causing long delays.  [0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The original page‐tree check [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`checkPages`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m had no cycle or depth guard, [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mrisking deep or cyclic page‐tree traversal.[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Patch details  [0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - **EndstreamFilterStream.java**  [0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • Added  [0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       `private static final long MAX_STREAM_SCAN = [0m[1;36m10[0m[39m * [0m[1;36m1024[0m[39m * [0m[1;36m1024[0m[39m;`  [0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • Changed the `[0m[1;35mfilter[0m[1;39m([0m[39mbyte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[39m b, int off, int len[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` condition from  [0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       `if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mpos == [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m && len > [0m[1;36m10[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`  [0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       to  [0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       `if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m([0m[39mlong[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m pos + len > MAX_STREAM_SCAN[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`  [0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • Purpose: disable filtering [0m[1;39m([0m[39mi.e. break out[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m once the scanned bytes exceed [0m[1;36m10[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mMB.  [0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - **PDFParser.java**  [0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • Added imports:  [0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       `java.util.Set`, `java.util.HashSet`,  [0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       `org.apache.pdfbox.cos.COSObject`,  [0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       `org.apache.pdfbox.cos.COSObjectKey`,  [0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       `org.apache.pdfbox.cos.COSArray`.  [0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • Defined constants:  [0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       `MAX_PAGE_DEPTH = [0m[1;36m1000[0m[39m`, `MAX_PAGE_NODES = [0m[1;36m5000[0m[39m`.  [0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • Replaced call to `[0m[1;35mcheckPages[0m[1;39m([0m[39mroot[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` with `[0m[1;35msafeCheckPages[0m[1;39m([0m[39mroot[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`.  [0m           [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       ```[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m===[0m[33mIssue[0m[39m===[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mERROR: libFuzzer: timeout[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m===Evaluation [0m[33mReport[0m[39m===[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m# Evaluation Report[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Summary[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe initial issue is a persistent libFuzzer timeout when exercising the PDF parser [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcode. A patch was introduced in two areas:  [0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. In EndstreamFilterStream.filter, a `MAX_STREAM_SCAN` limit [0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m10[0m[39m MB[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m was added to [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprevent unbounded scanning of input when looking for the “endstream” marker.  [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. In PDFParser, a new `safeCheckPages` routine replaces the unbounded `checkPages`[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcall, imposing limits on page-tree depth [0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m1[0m[39m [0m[1;36m000[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m and total nodes [0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m5[0m[39m [0m[1;36m000[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m and [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mguarding against cycles.[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAfter applying these changes, the fuzzer still reports the same “ERROR: libFuzzer: [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtimeout” without any change in behavior.[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Description[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Initial Issue  [0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The fuzzer run ends with “ERROR: libFuzzer: timeout.”  [0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - No stack trace or exception is reported; the parser appears to hang or loop [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mrather than crash.  [0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The harness simply feeds random or mutated bytes to the PDF parser entry [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpoint, and the timeout suggests unbounded work on certain inputs.[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Observations on the Initial Issue  [0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The hang is not tied to a specific exception or invalid PDF structure reported[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mback.  [0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The timeout implies at least one loop or recursive traversal fails to [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mterminate promptly under fuzzed input.  [0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Two likely hotspots for unbounded work are the endstream-marker scan in the [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfilter stream and the page tree recursion in PDFParser.[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Patch Attempt Details  [0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   A. EndstreamFilterStream.java  [0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - Introduced:  [0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m          private static final long MAX_STREAM_SCAN = [0m[1;36m10[0m[39m * [0m[1;36m1024[0m[39m * [0m[1;36m1024[0m[39m; [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m [0m[1;36m10[0m[39m MB [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcap  [0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - Changed the top-level filter condition:  [0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        From:  [0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m          if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mpos == [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m && len > [0m[1;36m10[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m[39m … [0m[1;39m}[0m[39m  [0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        To:  [0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m          if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m([0m[39mlong[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m pos + len > MAX_STREAM_SCAN[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m[39m  [0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m             mustFilter = false;  [0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m             …  [0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m          [0m[1;39m}[0m[39m  [0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - Goal: abort fallback filtering when the stream scan exceeds [0m[1;36m10[0m[39m MB.  [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   B. PDFParser.java  [0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - Added imports for COSObjectKey, COSArray, Set/HashSet.  [0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - Replaced direct call to `[0m[1;35mcheckPages[0m[1;39m([0m[39mroot[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` with `[0m[1;35msafeCheckPages[0m[1;39m([0m[39mroot[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`.  [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - Introduced constants:  [0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m          MAX_PAGE_DEPTH = [0m[1;36m1000[0m[39m  [0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m          MAX_PAGE_NODES = [0m[1;36m5000[0m[39m  [0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - `safeCheckPages` builds a visited key set and calls `[0m[1;35mcheckPagesRec[0m[1;39m([0m[39mnode, [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mvisited, depth[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`.  [0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - `checkPagesRec` throws `[0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Page tree too deep or too many [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [32mnodes…"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` if limits are exceeded.  [0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - Recursion proceeds only on COSDictionary nodes of type PAGES, tracking [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdepth and visited object keys.[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   C. Patch Result  [0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - After recompilation and re-running the libFuzzer harness, the same timeout [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39merror occurs with no additional output.[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Areas for Further Investigation  [0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - EndstreamFilterStream.filter logic beyond the new boundary check:  [0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • Verify how `pos` is updated and whether the loop can still become [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39meffectively infinite on crafted inputs  [0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • Check interactions with `mustFilter` and downstream buffer-reading code  [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - PDFParser page-tree traversal on fuzz inputs:  [0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • Ensure `safeCheckPages` is invoked on all code paths exercised by the fuzzer[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39minitialParse vs. incremental parsing[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • Confirm that `safeCheckPages` cannot itself be delayed indefinitely by [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmalformed structures before reaching the limit  [0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Any other recursive or loop-based parsers [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g., XRef table scanning, stream [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mobject decoding[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m that may lack similar safeguards  [0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Overall control flow under fuzz inputs to find which code region consumes [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mexcessive time leading to timeout.[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Initial Issue Log[0m                                                                [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_snippets[0m[39m>[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Endstream scanning cap in COSParser:[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   a. Introduce a new constant in COSParser [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`MAX_ENDSTREAM_SCAN = [0m[1;36m10[0m[39m * [0m[1;36m1024[0m[39m * [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1024[0m[39m`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m to mirror the [0m[1;36m10[0m[39m MB cap.[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   b. Locate the method that reads until “endstream” [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g., `readUntilEndStream` or[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`parseCOSStream`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m where the loop reads chunks into `strmBuf` and calls [0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mfilter.filter[0m[1;39m([0m[33m...[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`.[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   c. Add a cumulative counter `bytesScanned` initialized to [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m before the loop.[0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   d. In each iteration, after reading `readLen = [0m[1;35msource.read[0m[1;39m([0m[39mstrmBuf[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`, increment [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`bytesScanned += readLen`.[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   e. Immediately after incrementing, check `if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mbytesScanned > MAX_ENDSTREAM_SCAN[0m[1;39m)[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthrow new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Exceeded maximum endstream scan limit [0m[32m([0m[32m"[0m[39m + [0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mMAX_ENDSTREAM_SCAN + [0m[32m" bytes[0m[32m)[0m[32m"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;`[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   f. This ensures the loop cannot spin forever on malformed inputs lacking an [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m“endstream” marker.[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Correct and activate MAX_STREAM_SCAN in EndstreamFilterStream [0m[1;39m([0m[39moptional but [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mrecommended[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   a. In `EndstreamFilterStream`, ensure the `pos` or `length` field is incremented[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mon every `[0m[1;35mfilter[0m[1;39m([0m[33m...[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` invocation [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g., `length += len; pos = [0m[1;39m([0m[39mint[0m[1;39m)[0m[39mlength;`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   b. Replace the existing `if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m([0m[39mlong[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m pos + len > MAX_STREAM_SCAN[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` block with a [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcheck that throws `IOException` rather than silently disabling `mustFilter`. This [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprevents silent bypass of filtering and makes the cap explicit.[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   c. Example inside `[0m[1;35mfilter[0m[1;39m([0m[33m...[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`:[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      ```[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      length += len;[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlength > MAX_STREAM_SCAN[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m          throw new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Endstream scan exceeds "[0m[39m + MAX_STREAM_SCAN + [0m[32m" [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [32mbytes, aborting"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      ```[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   d. This change reinforces the cap at the stream-filter level and prevents [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39maccumulation of unbounded data in the internal buffer.[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Enforce safe page-tree traversal in PDFParser:[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   a. Add the `[0m[1;35msafeCheckPages[0m[1;39m([0m[39mCOSDictionary root[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` and its helper [0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mcheckPagesRec[0m[1;39m([0m[33m...[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` exactly as defined in the last patch attempt.[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   b. Replace every direct invocation of `[0m[1;35mcheckPages[0m[1;39m([0m[39mroot[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` with [0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35msafeCheckPages[0m[1;39m([0m[39mroot[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`. At minimum, modify in:[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - `[0m[1;35minitialParse[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`: change `[0m[1;35mcheckPages[0m[1;39m([0m[39mroot[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` to `[0m[1;35msafeCheckPages[0m[1;39m([0m[39mroot[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`.[0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - Any other entry points [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g., in incremental or lenient parsing paths[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m that[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mstill call `checkPages`.[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   c. Import required classes: `java.util.Set`, `java.util.HashSet`, [0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`org.apache.pdfbox.cos.COSObjectKey`, `org.apache.pdfbox.cos.COSArray`, etc.[0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Validate integration:[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   a. Ensure the parser still honors explicit stream lengths: streams with valid [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[35m/[0m[95mLength[0m[39m` entries bypass the endstream read-loop and use length-based slicing.[0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   b. Run existing unit and integration tests to confirm no regressions.[0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   c. Re-run libFuzzer: timeouts should now be replaced by `IOException` on overly [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlarge scans or deep page trees, terminating the parse promptly.[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mJustification:[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Enforcing the cap at the COSParser level guarantees that the main read-loop [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcannot spin indefinitely when “endstream” is missing, directly addressing the [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlibFuzzer timeout.[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Throwing an `IOException` is consistent with parser behavior on malformed data [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mand won’t hide other errors.[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Replacing all `checkPages` calls ensures page-tree recursion is bounded [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39meverywhere, preventing another potential hang on cyclic or excessively large page [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mstructures.[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Keeping the cap value aligned [0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m10[0m[39m MB, [0m[33mdepth[0m[39m=[0m[1;36m1000[0m[39m, [0m[33mnodes[0m[39m=[0m[1;36m5000[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m preserves the [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39moriginal patch intent while actually activating the safeguards.[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- This approach preserves correct parsing of well-formed PDFs [0m[1;39m([0m[39mwhich normally [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdeclare stream lengths and have reasonable page trees[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m and applies only to [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmalformed or malicious inputs that currently cause unbounded work.[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Tests and existing functionality remain intact, as valid PDFs will not exceed [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthese generous caps. [0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mfix_strategy[0m[1m>[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ===Evaluation [33mEnd[0m===                                                                [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39mERROR: libFuzzer: timeout[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m===Evaluation [0m[33mReport[0m[39m===[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m# Evaluation Report[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Summary[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAn initial libFuzzer run on PDFBox hung until a timeout. To prevent excessive [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprocessing during “endstream” scanning and page‐tree traversal, a patch was [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mproposed that:[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- In EndstreamFilterStream.java, introduces a `MAX_STREAM_SCAN` cap and throws an [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`IOException` if more than [0m[1;36m10[0m[39m MB of stream data is scanned.[0m                         [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m37[0m[39m:     * specified byte array starting at offset off to this output stream,[0m        [2m                [0m
