[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpdfbox/src/main/java/org/apache/pdfbox/pdfparser/PDFParser.jav[0m[1;92ma:19[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m28[0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m19[0m[39m:import java.io.File;[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m20[0m[39m:import java.io.IOException;[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m21[0m[39m:import java.io.InputStream;[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m22[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m23[0m[39m:import org.apache.logging.log4j.Logger;[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m24[0m[39m:import org.apache.logging.log4j.LogManager;[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m25[0m[39m:import org.apache.pdfbox.Loader;[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m26[0m[39m:import org.apache.pdfbox.cos.COSDictionary;[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m27[0m[39m:import org.apache.pdfbox.cos.COSName;[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m28[0m[39m:import org.apache.pdfbox.io.IOUtils;[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code>[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpdfbox/src/main/java/org/apache/pdfbox/pdfparser/PDFParser.jav[0m[1;92ma:34[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m37[0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m34[0m[39m:public class PDFParser extends COSParser[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m35[0m[39m:[0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m36[0m[39m:    private static final Logger LOG = [0m[1;35mLogManager.getLogger[0m[1;39m([0m[39mPDFParser.class[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m37[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code>[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpdfbox/src/main/java/org/apache/pdfbox/pdfparser/PDFParser.jav[0m[1;92ma:118[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m123[0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m118[0m[39m:        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m119[0m[39m:        [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m check pages dictionaries[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m120[0m[39m:        [0m[1;35mcheckPages[0m[1;39m([0m[39mroot[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m121[0m[39m:        [0m[1;35mdocument.setDecrypted[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m122[0m[39m:        initialParseDone = true;[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m123[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_snippets[0m[39m>[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. EndstreamFilterStream.java: Correct file header and insert stream‐scan cap[0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   a. Revert the accidental removal of the opening comment delimiter. Ensure lines [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m–[0m[1;36m15[0m[39m remain exactly as the original license block:[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      ```[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      [0m[35m/[0m[39m*[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       * Copyright [0m[1;36m2014[0m[39m The Apache Software Foundation.[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       * [0m[33m...[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       * limitations under the License.[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       *[0m[35m/[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      ```[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   b. Immediately after the license [0m[1;39m([0m[39mafter line [0m[1;36m15[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, verify the package declaration[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mis present:[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      ```[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      package org.apache.pdfbox.pdfparser;[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      ```[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   c. Directly below the package statement, insert the `IOException` import:[0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      ```[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      import java.io.IOException;[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      ```[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   d. Inside the `EndstreamFilterStream` class, locate the existing field [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdeclarations:[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      ```[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      private boolean hasCR = false;[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      private boolean hasLF = false;[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      private int pos = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      private boolean mustFilter = true;[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      private long length = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      ```[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      and insert a new static cap constant immediately after `length`:[0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      ```[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      private static final long MAX_STREAM_SCAN = 10L * [0m[1;36m1024[0m[39m * [0m[1;36m1024[0m[39m; [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m [0m[1;36m10[0m[39m MB cap[0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      ```[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   e. Update the `[0m[1;35mfilter[0m[1;39m([0m[39mbyte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[39m b, int off, int len[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` signature to declare `throws [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mIOException`:[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      ```[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      public void [0m[1;35mfilter[0m[1;39m([0m[39mbyte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[39m b, int off, int len[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m throws IOException[0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      ```[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   f. At the very start of the method body [0m[1;39m([0m[39mimmediately after the `[0m[1;39m{[0m[39m`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, add logic [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mto accumulate `length` and enforce the cap:[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      ```[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      length += len;[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlength > MAX_STREAM_SCAN[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m          throw new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Endstream scan exceeds cap of "[0m[39m [0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m              + MAX_STREAM_SCAN + [0m[32m" bytes, aborting"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      ```[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   This ensures that no more than [0m[1;36m10[0m[39m MB of stream data is processed and prevents [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39minfinite loops in endstream scanning.[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. PDFParser.java: Guard against deep or cyclic page trees[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   a. In the import section [0m[1;39m([0m[39mafter existing imports through [0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`org.apache.pdfbox.cos.COSName;` and before any blank line[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, add:[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      ```[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      import java.util.Set;[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      import java.util.HashSet;[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      import org.apache.pdfbox.cos.COSBase;[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      import org.apache.pdfbox.cos.COSObject;[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      import org.apache.pdfbox.cos.COSObjectKey;[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      import org.apache.pdfbox.cos.COSArray;[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      ```[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   b. Find the static `Logger` declaration:[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      ```[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      private static final Logger LOG = [0m[1;35mLogManager.getLogger[0m[1;39m([0m[39mPDFParser.class[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      ```[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      and immediately below add depth/node‐count safeguards:[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      ```[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      private static final int MAX_PAGE_DEPTH = [0m[1;36m1000[0m[39m;[0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      private static final int MAX_PAGE_NODES = [0m[1;36m5000[0m[39m;[0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      ```[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   c. In `[0m[1;35minitialParse[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` replace the unguarded page‐tree check:[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      ```[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m check pages dictionaries[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      [0m[1;35mcheckPages[0m[1;39m([0m[39mroot[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      ```[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      with:[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      ```[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m guard against cyclic or overly deep page trees[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      [0m[1;35msafeCheckPages[0m[1;39m([0m[39mroot[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      ```[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   d. Below `[0m[1;35minitialParse[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mor at the end of the class[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, implement the safe [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtraversal:[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      ```[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      private void [0m[1;35msafeCheckPages[0m[1;39m([0m[39mCOSDictionary root[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m throws IOException [0m[1;39m{[0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m          Set<COSObjectKey> visited = new HashSet<>[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m          [0m[1;35mcheckPagesRec[0m[1;39m([0m[39mroot, visited, [0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      private void [0m[1;35mcheckPagesRec[0m[1;39m([0m[39mCOSDictionary node,[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                                 Set<COSObjectKey> visited,[0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                                 int depth[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m throws IOException [0m[1;39m{[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m          if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mdepth > MAX_PAGE_DEPTH || [0m[1;35mvisited.size[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m > MAX_PAGE_NODES[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m              throw new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Page tree too deep or too many nodes, aborting[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [32mparse"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m          [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m          COSName type = [0m[1;35mnode.getCOSName[0m[1;39m([0m[39mCOSName.TYPE[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m          if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mCOSName.PAGES.equals[0m[1;39m([0m[39mtype[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m              COSBase kids = [0m[1;35mnode.getDictionaryObject[0m[1;39m([0m[39mCOSName.KIDS[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m              if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mkids instanceof COSArray[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                  for [0m[1;39m([0m[39mCOSBase kid : [0m[1;39m([0m[39mCOSArray[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m kids[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                      if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mkid instanceof COSObject[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                          COSObjectKey key = [0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m([0m[39mCOSObject[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m kid[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.getKey[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                          if [0m[1;39m([0m[39m![0m[1;35mvisited.add[0m[1;39m([0m[39mkey[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                              continue;[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                          [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                          COSBase child = [0m[1;35mdereferenceCOSObject[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m([0m[39mCOSObject[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m kid[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                          if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mchild instanceof COSDictionary[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                              [0m[1;35mcheckPagesRec[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m([0m[39mCOSDictionary[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m child, visited, depth +[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                          [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                      [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                  [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m              [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m          [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      ```[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   This logic maintains the existing `checkPages` behavior but enforces a recursion[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlimit [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`MAX_PAGE_DEPTH`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m and total node visits [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`MAX_PAGE_NODES`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, preventing [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mendless traversal on malformed page trees.[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Justification and Preservation of Logic[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - By restoring the original comment block and placing `package` and `import` [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mstatements in their legally sanctioned positions, we eliminate the “class, [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39minterface, or enum expected” compiler errors.[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The `MAX_STREAM_SCAN` cap addresses the original hang/timelock on “endstream” [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprocessing, while preserving the byte‐filtering logic [0m[1;39m([0m[39mthe `mustFilter` heuristics [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mremain unchanged once the cap check passes[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The `safeCheckPages` methods preserve existing PDF page‐tree validation [0m[1;39m([0m[39mby [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39minvoking the original recursive logic[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m but add boundary checks to break on [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mexcessively deep or cyclic structures.[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - All existing functionality—including ASCII detection in `[0m[1;35mfilter[0m[1;39m([0m[33m...[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`, [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdocument decryption, and subsequent parsing steps—remains intact.[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - No harness code, tests, or external dependencies are modified. All new code is[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mconfined within the two source files under `pdfparser`, ensuring compatibility with[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mexisting test suites and fuzzing entry points.[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Side‐effects and Mitigation[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - IOException will now surface sooner on extremely large streams or deep page [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtrees; calling code should already handle IOExceptions [0m[1;39m([0m[39mthe parser catches and [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mreports them[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Boundary constants [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`[0m[1;36m10[0m[39m MB`, `[0m[1;36m1[0m[39m [0m[1;36m000[0m[39m` depth, `[0m[1;36m5[0m[39m [0m[1;36m000[0m[39m` nodes[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m can be tuned if too[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mconservative; they are encapsulated as static fields for easy adjustment.[0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - No broad exceptions are caught, so genuine parsing errors still bubble up as [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbefore.[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThis patch resolves the compilation errors, prevents infinite loops in both [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mend‐stream filtering and page‐tree traversal, and retains the original filtering [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msemantics.[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mfix_strategy[0m[1m>[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ===Evaluation [33mEnd[0m===                                                                [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39mstreamLength[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m-            [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m-                [0m[1;35mdic.setLong[0m[1;39m([0m[39mCOSName.LENGTH, streamLength[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m-            [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+            [0m[1;35mdic.setLong[0m[1;39m([0m[39mCOSName.LENGTH, streamLength[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         String endStream = [0m[1;35mreadString[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mendStream.equals[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"endobj"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m && isLenient[0m[1;39m)[0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m===Patch [0m[33mResult[0m[39m===[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mERROR: libFuzzer: timeout[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m===[0m[33mIssue[0m[39m===[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mERROR: libFuzzer: timeout[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m===Evaluation [0m[33mReport[0m[39m===[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m# Evaluation Report[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Summary[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe project is exhibiting libFuzzer timeouts when parsing certain PDF inputs. To [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmitigate potential infinite or excessively long processing paths, a patch was [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mintroduced in two areas:[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. In EndstreamFilterStream, a [0m[1;36m10[0m[39m MB cap [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`MAX_STREAM_SCAN`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m and an `IOException` [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthrow were added to break out of overly long stream scans.[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. In PDFParser, the existing `checkPages` call was replaced by `safeCheckPages`, [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwhich tracks visited page‐tree nodes and enforces limits on recursion depth [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39m`MAX_PAGE_DEPTH = [0m[1;36m1000[0m[39m`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m and total nodes [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`MAX_PAGE_NODES = [0m[1;36m5000[0m[39m`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAfter applying these changes, libFuzzer still reports a timeout and no new [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mexception is observed in the logs.[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Description[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mInitial issue  [0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The libFuzzer harness repeatedly times out when exercising the PDFBox parser on [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcertain inputs.  [0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The log simply shows `ERROR: libFuzzer: timeout`, indicating that execution did [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mnot complete within the allotted time. No stack trace or exception is presented.  [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The harness triggers the normal parsing flow; the timeout suggests an infinite [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mloop or excessively long scan in one of the parser components.[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mPatch attempt  [0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. **EndstreamFilterStream.java**  [0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Imported `java.io.IOException`.  [0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Introduced a new static constant:  [0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     private static final long MAX_STREAM_SCAN = 10L * [0m[1;36m1024[0m[39m * [0m[1;36m1024[0m[39m; [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m [0m[1;36m10[0m[39m MB cap[0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```  [0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Updated `[0m[1;35mfilter[0m[1;39m([0m[39mbyte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[39m b, int off, int len[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` signature to throw `IOException`.[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Added logic to accumulate `length += len` and, if `length` exceeds [0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`MAX_STREAM_SCAN`, immediately throw an `IOException` to abort further scanning.  [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. **PDFParser.java**  [0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Added imports for `Set`, `HashSet`, `COSBase`, `COSObject`, `COSObjectKey`, [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mand `COSArray`.  [0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Defined two new limits:  [0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     private static final int MAX_PAGE_DEPTH = [0m[1;36m1000[0m[39m;[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     private static final int MAX_PAGE_NODES = [0m[1;36m5000[0m[39m;[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```  [0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Replaced the original `[0m[1;35mcheckPages[0m[1;39m([0m[39mroot[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;` call with `[0m[1;35msafeCheckPages[0m[1;39m([0m[39mroot[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;`.  [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Implemented `[0m[1;35msafeCheckPages[0m[1;39m([0m[39mCOSDictionary root[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` that creates a [0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`HashSet<COSObjectKey>` and calls a new recursive method `checkPagesRec`.  [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - `checkPagesRec` tracks both recursion depth and total visited nodes, throwing [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39man `IOException` if either limit is exceeded. It also prevents revisiting the same [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`COSObjectKey`.  [0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mResult after patch  [0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Applying these changes does not alter the fuzzing outcome: libFuzzer still [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mreports `timeout`. No new exceptions or error messages are logged. The parser [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mappears to remain stuck or in a slow‐path that exceeds the fuzzer’s timeout [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthreshold.[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAreas for further investigation  [0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The implementation of `EndstreamFilterStream.filter`: verify that the `length` [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfield is properly initialized and updated, and that no other loops in that class [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcan hang or process unbounded data.  [0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The page‐tree traversal in `PDFParser`: confirm that all COS objects are [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcorrectly dereferenced and that there are no alternate paths that bypass the new [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`safeCheckPages` logic.  [0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Other filtering or decoding streams in the parser, especially those handling [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mnon-ASCII or compressed streams, which may contain loops or recursive calls without[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mexit conditions.  [0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The harness entry point and how it feeds data into the parser, to identify which [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmethods are actually being executed when the timeout occurs.[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Initial Issue Log[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mHere is the initial issue log of the codebase:[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<issue>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mERROR: libFuzzer: timeout[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95missue[0m[39m>[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Additional Issue Log[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mHere is the additional issue log after the last patch attempt:[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<additional_issue>[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mERROR: libFuzzer: timeout[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95madditional_issue[0m[39m>[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Notes[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- All patch attempts are applied to the initial codebase. Reapply the the previous [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpatches if needed.[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- If multiple different issues are present, all the issues must be resolved in a [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msingle patch attempt.[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Try different approaches to resolve the issues.[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m===Analysis [0m[33mReport[0m[39m===[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m# Analysis Report[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m20[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[39m**[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m21[0m[39m: * This class is only for the readUntilEndStream method, to prevent a final CR [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mLF or LF [0m[1;39m([0m[39mbut not a final CR![0m[1;39m)[0m[39m from being[0m                                           [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m23[0m[39m: * PDFBOX-[0m[1;36m2120[0m[39m and avoids making [0m[1;35mreadUntilEndStream[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m even more complex than it [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39malready is.[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m24[0m[39m: *[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m25[0m[39m: * @author Tilman Hausherr[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m26[0m[39m: *[0m[35m/[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;92m27:c[0m[39mlass EndstreamFilterStream[0m                                                      [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m32[0m[39m:    private boolean mustFilter = true;[0m                                           [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpdfbox/src/main/java/org/apache/pdfbox/pdfparser/EndstreamFilterStream.jav[0m[1;92ma:29[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m34[0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m29[0m[39m:    private boolean hasCR = false;[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m30[0m[39m:    private boolean hasLF = false;[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m31[0m[39m:    private int pos = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m32[0m[39m:    private boolean mustFilter = true;[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m33[0m[39m:    private long length = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m34[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code>[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpdfbox/src/main/java/org/apache/pdfbox/pdfparser/EndstreamFilterStream.jav[0m[1;92ma:44[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m80[0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m44[0m[39m:    public void [0m[1;35mfilter[0m[1;39m([0m[39mbyte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[39m b, int off, int len[0m[1;39m)[0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m45[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m46[0m[39m:        if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mpos == [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m && len > [0m[1;36m10[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m49[0m[39m:            mustFilter = false;[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m50[0m[39m:            for [0m[1;39m([0m[39mint i = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m; i < [0m[1;36m10[0m[39m; ++i[0m[1;39m)[0m                                         [2m                [0m
